<body>
<div><head>賀氏喪服要記</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.2">「出居廬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.3">論稱杖者必廬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.4">廬者必禫。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.5">此明杖章之內，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.6">居廬必禫。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.7">若別而言之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.8">則杖有不禫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.9">禫有不杖者。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.10">案〈小記〉篇云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.11">「宗子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.12">母在為妻禫。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.13">則其非宗子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.14">其餘適庶母在，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.15">為妻並不得禫也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.16">〈小記〉又云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.17">「父在，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.18">為妻以杖即位。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.19">鄭元云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.20">「庶子為妻。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.21">然父在為妻猶有其杖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.22">則父沒母存，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.23">有杖可知。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.24">此是杖有不禫者也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.25">〈小記〉篇云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.26">「庶子在父之室，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.27">則其為母不禫。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.28">若其不杖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.29">則〈喪服〉不杖之條，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.30">應有庶子為母不杖之文。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.31">今無其文，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.32">則猶杖可知也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.33">前文云「三年而后葬」者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.34">但有練、祥而無禫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.35">是有杖無禫。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.36">此二條是杖而不禫。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-1a.37">《禮記‧喪服小記》孔頴達《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.2">婦人尊微，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.3">不奪正服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.4">並厭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.5">其餘哀。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.6">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.7">〈小記〉云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.8">「久而不葬者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.9">唯主喪者不除。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.10">案〈服問〉曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.11">「君所主夫人、妻、太子、適婦」，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.12">故謂此在不除之例。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.13">同上引庾云，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.14">謂昔主，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-2a.15">〈要記〉案〈服問〉云云。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.2">〈小記〉云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.3">「與諸侯為兄弟者服斬。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.4">鄭《注》謂卿大夫以下也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.5">與尊者為親，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.6">不敢以輕服服之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.7">「言諸侯者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.8">明雖在異國，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.9">猶來為三年也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.10">案下〈雜記〉云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.11">「外宗為君大夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.12">如〈內宗〉。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.13">注云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.14">「謂嫁於國中者。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.15">此云「異國」，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.16">二注不同，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.17">按男子及婦人皆謂在國內者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.18">譙周亦以為然。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.19">同上。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.20">引賀循以鄭二注不同，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.21">故著《要記》云云經注，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.22">據補。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.23">在己國則得為君服斬夫人齊衰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.24">若在他國，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.25">則不得也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-3a.26">《禮記‧雜記下‧正義》引賀循、譙周。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a.2">婦人不杖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a.3">謂出嫁之婦人不為主，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a.4">則不杖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a.5">其不為主而杖者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a.6">唯姑在為夫杖，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a.7">故此〈記〉特明之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a.8">《禮記‧喪服小記‧正義》引賀循等。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a.9">慈母之子不服慈母之黨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a.10">婦又不從夫而服慈姑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a.11">小功服無從故也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-4a.12">《南史‧儒林‧司馬筠傳》周捨議引賀彥先。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.2">公子之二宗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.3">皆一代而已。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.4">庶兄弟既亡之後，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.5">各為一宗之祖也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.6">嫡繼其正統者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.7">各自為大宗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.8">乃成百代不遷之宗也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.9">杜佑《通典》卷七十三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.10">凡諸侯之嗣子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.11">繼代為君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.12">君之群弟不敢宗君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.13">君命其母弟為宗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.14">諸弟宗之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.15">亦謂之大宗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.16">死則為𪗋縗九月。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.17">若無母弟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.18">則命庶弟之大者為宗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.19">諸弟宗之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.20">亦如母弟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.21">則為之大功九月。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.22">此二宗者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.23">一代而已。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.24">庶兄弟既死之後，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.25">各為一宗之祖。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-5a.26">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.2">公之庶兄弟父卒為其母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.3">大夫之庶子父在為母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.4">皆大功九月。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.5">凡降服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.6">既降，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.7">心喪如常。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.8">又天子諸侯賤妾子為其母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.9">厭於父，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.10">不得制縗麤之服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.11">三月而葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.12">葬已而服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.13">居處飲食言語，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.14">心喪三年。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-6a.15">《通典》卷八十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-7a.2">諸侯女以為天子后，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-7a.3">以尊還降其族人。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-7a.4">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-7a.5">天子諸侯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-7a.6">五屬之內，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-7a.7">雖不服職為臣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-7a.8">皆服斬縗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-7a.9">為夫人則𪗋縗周。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-7a.10">同上江霦引《賀公記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-8a.2">雖不立，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-8a.3">位在嫡正，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-8a.4">父之所繼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-8a.5">己之所承，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-8a.6">故為三年。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-8a.7">《通典》卷八十二侍中孔《注》引賀循。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-8a.8">母為長子𪗋縗三年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-8a.9">其服節如父為子者。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-8a.10">《通典》卷八十七魏顆引《要記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-9a.2">庶子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-9a.3">父雖沒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-9a.4">猶不為長子三年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-9a.5">以己不繼祖也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-9a.6">《通典》卷八十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-9a.7">按〈小記〉為祖母後者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-9a.8">服之如母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-9a.9">不為祖父母後者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-9a.10">不得為祖母三年。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-9a.11">《通典》卷八十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a" ed="CHANT" n="001-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.2">父在為母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.3">厭尊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.4">故屈而從周。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.5">出母服不減者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.6">以本既降，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.7">義無再厭故也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.8">父在為母既已杖矣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.9">若父在母出宜重降者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.10">則宜不杖條。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.11">今在杖條，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.12">明不再降。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.13">杖者不居廬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.14">居廬必禫。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-10a.15">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a" ed="CHANT" n="001-11a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.2">老疾三諫去者為舊君服𪗋縗。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.3">《通典》卷九十引王肅、賀循，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.4">又引云王賀《要記》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.5">按鄭注〈喪服〉云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.6">「凡妻從夫降一等。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.7">夫合三月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.8">則妻宜無服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.9">而猶三月者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.10">古者大夫不外娶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.11">其妻則本國之女也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.12">雖後夫而出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.13">婦人歸宗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.14">往來，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.15">故從人服也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.16">長子有服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.17">謂未去者也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.18">循以為以道去君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.19">非罪之重，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.20">其子尚可以留，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.21">值君薨則服也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-11a.22">《通典》卷九十。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a" ed="CHANT" n="001-12a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a.2">庶母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a.3">士父之妾也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a.4">服緦麻。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a.5">大夫以上無服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a.6">按馬融引喪服云，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a.7">大夫以上庶母無服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a.8">《通典》卷九十二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a.9">為乳母緦三月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a.10">士與大夫皆同，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a.11">不以尊卑降功服故也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-12a.12">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a" ed="CHANT" n="001-13a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.2">大夫妻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.3">其娣姒其夫為士，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.4">服亦降一等。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.5">《通典》卷九十三。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.6">諸侯於其旁親，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.7">一無所服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.8">唯父母、妻、長子、長子之妻及為父之後者、姑姊妹嫁於諸侯及始封之君所未臣諸父昆弟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.9">皆以其服服之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.10">大夫為其外親為士者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.11">尊雖不同，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.12">亦不降。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.13">大夫女為國夫人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.14">唯父母及昆弟為父後者不降。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.15">士女為大夫妻者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.16">不降高祖、曾祖、祖、父母、兄弟為父後者及大宗而已。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-13a.17">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a" ed="CHANT" n="001-14a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a.2">庶子服出母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a.3">父在服𪗋縗周，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a.4">父沒不服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a.5">《通典》卷九十四殷仲堪引王賀首句，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a.6">據殷補。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a.7">庶子為人後，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a.8">為其母緦麻三月。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a.9">庶子之妻自如常禮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a.10">尊所不降也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a.11">自天子通於大夫皆然。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-14a.12">《通典》卷九十五。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-15a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-15a" ed="CHANT" n="001-15a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-15a.2">其夫為祖、曾祖、高祖後者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-15a.3">妻從服如舅。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-15a.4">𪗋縗周也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-15a.5">《通典》卷九十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-15a.6">出母出。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-15a.7">當以捨此適彼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-15a.8">不獨在嫁。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-15a.9">同上。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-15a.10">孔德澤引。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a" ed="CHANT" n="001-16a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.2">父之喪服未竟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.3">又遭母喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.4">當父服應竟之月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.5">皆服祥祭之服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.6">如除喪之禮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.7">卒事，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.8">反母之喪服也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.9">《通典》卷九十七。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.10">「父未殯而祖亡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.11">承嫡猶周，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.12">此不忍變父在也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.13">故自用父在服母之禮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-16a.14">靈筵不得終三年也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-17a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-17a" ed="CHANT" n="001-17a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-17a.2">父死未殯而祖父死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-17a.3">祖以周；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-17a.4">既殯而祖父死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-17a.5">三年。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-17a.6">此謂嫡子為父後者也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-17a.7">父未殯服祖以周者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-17a.8">父屍尚在，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-17a.9">人子之義，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-17a.10">未可以代重也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a" ed="CHANT" n="001-18a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.2">雖有父母之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.3">皆為周大功之服祥除，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.4">各服其降喪之服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.5">如常除之節。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.6">小功已下則不除，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.7">轉輕也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.8">降而為小功則除之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.9">生於他方，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.10">不及見祖父母、諸父、昆弟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.11">若聞喪之日，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.12">月已過，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.13">不為稅服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.14">以未嘗相見恩情輕也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.15">若日月未過，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.16">服之如常。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-18a.17">並同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-19a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-19a" ed="CHANT" n="001-19a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-19a.2">小功不稅者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-19a.3">謂喪月都竟乃聞喪者耳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-19a.4">若在服內，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-19a.5">則自全五月。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-19a.6">《通典》卷九十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-19a.7">周則沒閏。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-19a.8">《通典》卷一百王儉《議》引鄭、射、王賀。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a" ed="CHANT" n="001-20a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.2">如朋友之禮。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.3">異者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.4">雖出行，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.5">猶絰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.6">所以尊師也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.7">按《禮記》：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.8">「夫子之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.9">門人疑所服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.10">子貢曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.11">『昔夫子喪顏回，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.12">若喪子而無服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.13">請喪夫子若喪父而無服。』<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.14">於是門人廬于墓所，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.15">心喪三年。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.16">蓋師徒之恩重也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.17">無服者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.18">謂無正喪之服也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.19">孔子之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.20">二三子皆絰而出。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.21">注曰「為師也」。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.22">然則凡弔服加麻者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.23">出則變服矣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-20a.24">《通典》卷一百一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-21a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-21a" ed="CHANT" n="001-21a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-21a.2">改葬服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-21a.3">鄭元云三月者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-21a.4">以親覩屍柩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-21a.5">故三月以序其餘懷。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-21a.6">但遲速不可限，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-21a.7">故不在三月章也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-21a.8">《通典》卷一百二賀循答傅純引鄭元說以為鄭得從重。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-21a.9">故《要記》從之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-21a.10">據補。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a" ed="CHANT" n="001-22a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.2">始弔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.3">朝服元端之服也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.4">皮弁絰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.5">素弁而加環絰也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.6">始死而往朝服者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.7">主人未變，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.8">賓未可以變也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.9">《太平御覽》卷五百六十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.10">占之弔者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.11">皆因朝夕哭而入弔。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.12">賓至，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.13">主人即出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.14">中門外，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.15">西面，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.16">北上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.17">拜。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.18">賓入門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.19">即位於堂下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.20">阼階，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.21">西面。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.22">賓入，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.23">即位，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.24">皆哭。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.25">哭止，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-22a.26">主人拜之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a" ed="CHANT" n="001-23a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.2">大夫弔於大夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.3">始死而往，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.4">朝服裼裘，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.5">如吉時也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.6">當斂之時而至，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.7">則弁絰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.8">服皮弁之服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.9">以襲裘也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.10">主人成服而往，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.11">則皮弁絰而加錫衰也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.12">大夫於士有朋友之恩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.13">乃得弁絰。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1086_CHANT_001-23a.14">並同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
